CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 7, 1962, page 8, reads: "Cutting Cake - Mr. and Mrs. Leroy Townsend cut their wedding cake at the reception which followed their recent marriage at Calvary Baptist Church. The bride is the former Mrs. Mildred Burgess. The Rev. James A. Cox, assisted by the Rev. Robert Brown, officiated at the rites. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Bride, Mildred Townsend wearing short floral veil and light colored jacquard suit, standing with groom, Leroy Townsend in wedding receiving line in Calvary Baptist Church for Townsend Burgess wedding
